    <item>
      <title>非营利性医院的首席执行官收入颇丰。但这对患者有好处吗？</title>
      <link>https://www.npr.org/sections/shots-health-news/2024/08/19/nx-s1-5078495/nonprofit-hospitals-ceo-compensation-community-benefit-uninsured-mission-tax-exempt-management</link>
      <description><![CDATA[非营利性医院给首席执行官的薪酬非常丰厚，而且薪酬不断上涨。一些研究人员怀疑，不断上涨的薪酬是否符合患者和纳税人的最佳利益。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.npr.org/sections/shots-health-news/2024/08/19/nx-s1-5078495/nonprofit-hospitals-ceo-compensation-community-benefit-uninsured-mission-tax-exempt-management</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 19 Aug 2024 09:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
