    <item>
      <title>印第安纳州计划旨在帮助坐轮椅的儿童克服人行道障碍</title>
      <link>https://www.npr.org/2024/08/19/nx-s1-5066921/indiana-program-aims-to-help-children-in-wheelchairs-overcome-sidewalk-obstacles</link>
      <description><![CDATA[《美国残疾人法案》签署近 35 年后，许多路缘坡道和人行道仍然不适合轮椅通行。印第安纳州的一项计划帮助儿童克服这些障碍。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.npr.org/2024/08/19/nx-s1-5066921/indiana-program-aims-to-help-children-in-wheelchairs-overcome-sidewalk-obstacles</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 19 Aug 2024 08:44:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
